	<longdescription>TNT==========**TNT** is a library for PyTorch **t**rai**n**ing **t**ools and utilities.&lt;p align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/pytorch/tnt/actions?query=branch%3Amaster&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/github/actions/workflow/status/pytorch/tnt/test.yml?branch=master&quot; alt=&quot;build status&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://pypi.org/project/torchtnt&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/torchtnt&quot; alt=&quot;pypi version&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://pypi.org/project/torchtnt-nightly&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/torchtnt-nightly?label=nightly&quot; alt=&quot;pypi nightly version&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://codecov.io/gh/pytorch/tnt&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://codecov.io/gh/pytorch/tnt/branch/master/graph/badge.svg?token=DR67Q6T7YF&quot; alt=&quot;codecov&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://github.com/pytorch/tnt/blob/master/LICENSE&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/pypi/l/torchtnt&quot; alt=&quot;bsd license&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://pytorch.org/tnt/&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;https://img.shields.io/badge/dynamic/json.svg?label=docs&amp;url=https%3A%2F%2Fpypi.org%2Fpypi%2Ftorchtnt%2Fjson&amp;query=%24.info.version&amp;colorB=brightgreen&amp;prefix=v&quot; alt=&quot;documentation status&quot;&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;## InstallationTNT can be installed with pip. To do so, run:```buildoutcfgpip install torchtnt```If you run into issues, make sure that Pytorch is installed first.You can also install the latest version from master. Just run:```buildoutcfgpip install git+https://github.com/pytorch/tnt.git@master```To update to the latest version from master:```buildoutcfgpip install --upgrade git+https://github.com/pytorch/tnt.git@master```</longdescription>
